<p>This is an expensive monitor, but Samsung’s build quality lives up to the price tag. The Neo G9 has a sleek, futuristic look and an impressive stand that keeps the monitor stable despite its weight. The monitor also has an attractive and intuitive on-screen menu that makes settings easy to change.</p>

